Use the Cloudmark Authority Engine (CMAE) for SpamAssassin.
Cloudmark has a nice API in the package mentioned above that
can be used for extremely accurate spam recognition.

Of course, you need a working (or trial) Cloudmark licence key,
see the following web address for details and for getting the
required packages:

http://www.cloudmark.com/serviceproviders/authority/spamassassin/trial/

